      <a href="http://www.upnp.org">UPnP</a> is a protocol stack that allows to communicate with devices over an IP network.
      This project focuses on an open implementation of the neccessary parts to build an UPnP-AV media server. 
      This consists of the following modules:
      <ul>
        <li><a href="mmm-upnp-ssdp/index.html">Discovery</a></li>
        <li><a href="mmm-upnp-description/index.html">Description</a></li>
        <li><a href="mmm-upnp-control/index.html">Control</a></li>
        <li><a href="mmm-upnp-notification/index.html">Notification</a></li>
        <li><a href="mmm-upnp-presentation/index.html">Presentation</a></li>
      </ul>
      </p>
